data.description: UPDATED HOME ON 1 ACRE IN HEART OF LITTLE ROCK! Nestled in a cul-de-sac, this home is situated on a quiet street with an acre lot…such a rare find. It is updated with stainless appliances, granite countertops, new luxury vinyl floors, new lighting, and fresh paint. In addition to the 3 bedrooms and 2 living rooms, there is also an office with built in cabinets and a large shop attached to the garage with a full bath. The shop space includes cabinets and benches but could also easily be finished out and made into living quarters. The screened in back porch is great for relaxing. Such a unique property!
